# Canonicalize www -> apex
https://www.mymechanicarizona.com/* https://mymechanicarizona.com/:splat 301!
http://www.mymechanicarizona.com/* https://mymechanicarizona.com/:splat 301!
http://mymechanicarizona.com/* https://mymechanicarizona.com/:splat 301!

# Trailing slash normalization (to match typical WordPress permalink style)
# If you prefer NO trailing slashes later, flip these rules.
# Note: Cloudflare Pages _redirects doesn't support regex; we handle most common patterns.
#/services/* /services/:splat/ 301


# Case normalization
/Services/* /services/:splat 301!

# Trailing slash for services
/services/* /services/:splat/ 301!
